<p>王鹤棣还会开玩笑跟她说“摸你猪头”，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200820/8355f79c001d4961b36e2485815e13e8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>还有各种同款鞋包，</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p9.itc.cn/images01/20200820/be692ee89bc647a0a94d5faaf21c6252.png" max-width="600" /></p>
